02:25:57.800 --> 02:25:59.110
blessed and you have a wonderful

02:25:59.120 --> 02:26:02.670
weekend, a wonderful week ahead, the rest

02:26:02.680 --> 02:26:06.070
of it. And as we start May 1st,

02:26:06.080 --> 02:26:09.030
right in the next 15 minutes,

02:26:09.040 --> 02:26:10.990
May 1st is here.

02:26:11.000 --> 02:26:13.390
Isn't Jesus wonderful? The fifth month

02:26:13.400 --> 02:26:19.350
of the year.

02:26:19.360 --> 02:26:23.990
How time flies, doesn't it?

02:26:24.000 --> 02:26:26.350
May

02:26:26.360 --> 02:26:30.030
going into June and July.

02:26:30.040 --> 02:26:32.870
This is the month that we pray

02:26:32.880 --> 02:26:34.030
for the nation. This is going to be

02:26:34.840 --> 02:26:38.430
a very pivotal month. May is a

02:26:38.440 --> 02:26:41.670
very important month. Remember that.

02:26:41.680 --> 02:26:43.750
So, we love y'all.

02:26:43.760 --> 02:26:45.670
Thank you for joining us. We'll end it

02:26:45.680 --> 02:26:46.910
here.

02:26:46.920 --> 02:26:49.310
Put a smile on your face

02:26:49.320 --> 02:26:51.510
and a song in your heart.

02:26:51.520 --> 02:26:53.950
Jesus loves you so much and we love you.

02:26:53.960 --> 02:26:55.630
God bless you and we'll see you again

02:26:55.640 --> 02:26:58.800
soon. Bye-bye.

